  "title": "An oval red and green UFO was spotted in Bandeirante-PR [1986]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/07/12/an-oval-red-and-green-ufo-was-spotted-in-bandeirante-pr-1986/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-1MC",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>JUNE 5th, 1986</strong>. Time: 20:00. Duration: not determined. A resident of the city of Bandeirante, in the north of Paraná, called CINDACTA II [Second Integrated Air Defense and Air Traffic Control Center], an agency of the Ministry of Aeronautics, to report the sighting of an unidentified flying object with an &#8220;oval&#8221; and flattened shape &#8220;emitting a&#8221; green and red light sequence &#8220;. The sighting, according to the witness, was also accompanied by other people.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.245. “Notícias sobre OVNI</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span>&lt;</p>\n",
